    "views": 67,
    "replies_count": 1
  },
  {
    "id": "17932603278288533",
    "text": "「高い整体より薬の方が早い」\nそれは本当でしょうか。",
    "timestamp": "2026-06-09T22:10:54+0000",
    "like_count": 0,
    "views": 520,
    "replies_count": 5
  },
  {
